# Compute-Heavy Trace
# Demonstrates high IPC through independent ALU operations
ADD R1 R2 R3
ADD R4 R5 R6
SUB R7 R8 R9
MUL R10 R11 R12
ADD R13 R14 R15
SUB R16 R17 R18
MUL R19 R20 R21
ADD R22 R23 R1
ADD R2 R3 R4
SUB R5 R6 R7
MUL R8 R9 R10
ADD R11 R12 R13
ADD R14 R15 R16
SUB R17 R18 R19
MUL R20 R21 R22
ADD R23 R1 R2
